caller_intent: Evelyn Gordon wants to cancel two insurance policies: an auto policy with National General and a homeowner's policy with Auto Owners Insurance.
resolution_steps: Agent asked for clarification on the types of policies Evelyn wanted to cancel.
Agent offered to transfer her to a specialist agent to handle the cancellation request.
knowledge_required: Understanding cancellation procedures for auto and homeowner's policies
Knowledge of carrier-specific requirements (National General, Auto Owners Insurance)
summary: Evelyn Gordon requested cancellation of two insurance policies. The agent collected policy details and initiated a transfer to a specialist agent to handle the cancellation. The call ended with the agent preparing to connect her to the appropriate team.
